Purpose
  Provide authoritative evidence that GreekTrustCo has formally appointed a Data Protection Officer (DPO) in accordance with GDPR (Articles 37–39) and applicable national law, and that the DPO’s role, independence, resources, and reporting line are explicitly established. This supports supervisory expectations for governance of personal data processing across Qualified Trust Services.

Required Properties of the Official Document
  - Format: PDF (non-password-protected; printable; PDF/A acceptable)
  - Language: Greek and/or English (Greek original preferred; an English translation may be appended in the same PDF)
  - Signatures: Signed by an authorized representative (per Articles of Association/ΓΕΜΗ); DPO countersignature recommended for acknowledgement
  - Effective Date: On or before submission date (2025-06-15)
